PKG_SHORTDESC="Media Metadata for Python"
PKG_LONGDESC="Kaa Metadata is a Media Meta Data retrieval framework. It retrieves metadata from mp3, ogg, avi, jpg, tiff and other file formats. Among others it thereby parses ID3v2, ID3v1, EXIF, IPTC and Vorbis data into an object oriented struture."
